data.description:
Amazing 2-story home sitting on a 1/4 acre lot; with potential to construct your own RV parking on the right side!
Step inside and be greeted by soaring high ceilings, creating an open and airy atmosphere making the space look even larger! 
Property boasts a generously sized backyard, perfect for hosting gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying some quality time with loved ones.
Cozy up by the fireplace on those chilly evenings, as this home features a unique two-way chimney, providing warmth and ambiance to both the living room and dining room. This property comes with a separate RV parking area, ensuring your beloved recreational vehicle has a safe and convenient space to call home. Property offers a two-car garage with additional room, ensuring you have plenty of space for all your belongings.
Convenience meets style with a Jack & Jill bathroom, connecting two bedrooms with a shared bathroom.
Don't miss this opportunity!
